org.opensha.calc.tasks

Class Tasks

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opensha.calc.tasks.Tasks

  • public final class Tasks
extends Object
    Factory class for creating the tasks that make up a hazard calculation. All methods return Callable instances.
    Author:
    Peter Powers
